title: Bunny Mania 2 HD v1.0.16
description:
Command lots of bunnies, and help them to reach the bunny house.
Build bridges, drill holes, and collect vegetables.

Try a classic puzzle game with HD graphics for tablets and phones!

Features:

- 4 game worlds, 60 levels
- 10 tools
- powerups and crates
- advanced hint system
- nice HD graphics with bunnies

What's new in version 1.0.16

- 3 stars rating fixed in few levels.
